channel.description: Identity Providers Click here to give feedback about this page About This Page Page ID: 784 Is this a new page?: New doc with new content but also pulling from existing content Target personas: Internal app builders, Saas Builder Description: This is a new doc defining what an identity provider is how Okta acts as one what an external identity provider is, and how an app and Okta interact with them (in overview - not very much detail - this is covered in Build > Federate Identities).
